title: Did Kyle Rittenhouse hit a woman in this video?
subtitle: A video of a battle in Kenosha, Wisconsin, supposedly shows the 17-year-old accused of killing two people in a demonstration of assault on a woman.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The 17-year-old video video of Kyle Rittenhouse, accused of killing two people in a protest in Kenosha, Wisconsin, shows a woman punch.
